By: Ibn al-Fârid
Commentary: According to Nâbulusî the commentator, this resplendence is
  the human intellect, which is a flash of the Primal Intelligence.
---
But for its perfume, I should not have found the way to its taverns：
and but for its resplendence, the imagination would not have pictured
it.
